== 開發 ==
在2013 [[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展期間, [[Microsoft_Studios|Microsoft Studios]]的副總裁[[Phil_Spencer|Phil Spencer]]說：出戰爭機器系列的續集是有可能性的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oxm.co.uk/56421/gears-of-war-xbox-one-will-take-some-time-says-microsoft/|title=Gears of War Xbox One will take "some time", says Microsoft|work=[[Official_Xbox_Magazine|Official Xbox Magazine]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|date=14 June 2013|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Edwin|last=Evans|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617014520/http://www.oxm.co.uk/56421/gears-of-war-xbox-one-will-take-some-time-says-microsoft/|archivedate=17 June 2013|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

2014年1月27號, 微軟宣布，他們已經購買了戰爭機器系列在Epic Games公司的專營權，以及新的戰爭機器系列將會由[[The_Coalition|The Coalition]]開發，並在[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]上發售。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2014/01/27/microsoft-acquires-gears-of-war-from-epic-assigns-next-game-to-black-tusk-studios/|title=Microsoft Acquires 'Gears of War' From Epic, Assigns Next Game To The Coalition|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|publisher=Forbes, Inc.|date=27 January 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Daniel Nye|last=Griffiths|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111204240/https://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2014/01/27/microsoft-acquires-gears-of-war-from-epic-assigns-next-game-to-black-tusk-studios/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/27/gears-of-war-rights-acquired-by-microsoft|title=Gears of War Rights Acquired by Microsoft|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=27 January 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Luke|last=Karmali|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117191158/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/27/gears-of-war-rights-acquired-by-microsoft|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Rod_Fergusson|Rod Fergusson]]原生產史詩遊戲主任特許經營，並對此遊戲產生出領導作用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/27/5345342/gears-of-war-xbox-one-microsoft-epic-games-rod-fergusson|title=Microsoft acquires Gears of War from Epic, hires series producer Rod Fergusson|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|date=27 January 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Michael|last=McWhertor|archive-date=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105042337/http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/27/5345342/gears-of-war-xbox-one-microsoft-epic-games-rod-fergusson|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/1/5958879/gears-of-war-black-tusk-rod-fergusson|title=The fixer: Why Rod Fergusson returned to Gears of War|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|date=1 August 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Brian|last=Crecente|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224130703/https://www.polygon.com/2014/8/1/5958879/gears-of-war-black-tusk-rod-fergusson|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.totalxbox.com/81168/features/epic-streak-rod-fergusson-on-bringing-gears-of-war-to-xbox-one/|title=Epic streak: Rod Fergusson on bringing Gears of War to Xbox One. Series veteran talks The Coalition, Bioshock and betraying fans|work=[[Official_Xbox_Magazine|Official Xbox Magazine]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|date=13 September 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Jon|last=Hicks|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913145434/http://www.totalxbox.com/81168/features/epic-streak-rod-fergusson-on-bringing-gears-of-war-to-xbox-one/|archivedate=13 September 2014|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 2015年4月1日，該系列的動畫及武器模型製作商Allie "JackFelling" Henze, 表示《戰爭機器4》不會在[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]上發售。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/04/01/the-next-gears-of-war-game-wont-come-to-xbox-360|title=The Next Gears of War Game Won't Come To Xbox 360|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=1 April 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Brian|last=Albert|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128224340/https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/04/01/the-next-gears-of-war-game-wont-come-to-xbox-360|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《戰爭機器4》从2016年4月18日起至5月1日进行了[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台的公測，並在之後宣布游戏将于2016年10月11日在全球同步上市。<ref>[http://uk.ign.com/articles/2016/03/15/gears-of-war-4-beta-dates-revealed GEARS OF WAR 4 BETA DATES REVEALED] {{Wayback|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2016/03/15/gears-of-war-4-beta-dates-revealed |date=20200120233304 }}.IGN.2016-03-15.[2016-09-15].</ref><ref>[http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/04/06/gears-of-war-4-release-date-and-cover-art-announced GEARS OF WAR 4 RELEASE DATE AND COVER ART ANNOUNCED] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/04/06/gears-of-war-4-release-date-and-cover-art-announced |date=20201108135202 }}.IGN.2016-04-06.[2016-09-15].</ref>

在[[E3_2016|2016年E3游戏展]]上，微软宣布《战争机器4》将支持Xbox One与Windows 10的跨平台计划“[[Xbox_Play_Anywhere游戏列表|Xbox Play Anywhere]]”，玩家在两个平台中任意一个上购买游戏会赠送游戏另一个平台的数字版本，此外玩家还可以通过该计划共享游戏存档进度和进行跨平台多人对战。<ref>[http://uk.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-gears-of-war-4-is-cross-buy-cross-play-on-xbox-one-windows-10 E3 2016: GEARS OF WAR 4 IS CROSS-BUY, CROSS-PLAY ON XBOX ONE, WINDOWS 10] {{Wayback|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-gears-of-war-4-is-cross-buy-cross-play-on-xbox-one-windows-10 |date=20160704133245 }}.IGN.2016-06-13.[2016-09-15].</ref>

